description:
UpIsNotJump Wasteland Survival Merch boxes are here:
https://PixelEmpire.com/UpIsNotJump

Join my patreon at $10 to get my cool poster with free shipping!
https://Patreon.com/upisnotjump

Once you join it will unlock full details on how to get the poster, it is all very simple!
 
Any tier will get you cool stuff tho, I have lots of leftovers from this video.

Anyway, hope you enjoyed this review of the Fallout TV show, I am a big fan of the show, and was happy to put a lot of hard work into reviewing it.  I will likely prioritize this show as a feature for the channel.
